<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://images-us.bookshop.org/ingram/9780063414006.jpg?height=500&amp;v=v2-d4cf35be14e6b9974a2494d17814b63d" alt="The Children of Jocasta - Haynes, Natalie" width="199" height="300" /></p>
