<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://images-us.bookshop.org/ingram/9780063353640.jpg?height=500&amp;v=v2-2e8790d0e19013432e266ce7a6c1b8ab" alt="How Does That Make You Feel, Magda Eklund? - Montague, Anna" width="200" height="300" /></p>
