</em>(Ecco Press)</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&#8220;A road trip novel with a tremendous amount of heartâ€”I ached along with the characters, rooted for them, wished them all the best. Truly a novel that asks you to consider the winding, secret path to love that sits lodged in every person&#8217;s breast. Anna Montague has written something bright and lovely here, a novel that is above all quietly beautiful.&#8221;<br />
